java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Cloneable, org.jfree.chart.LegendItemSource, org.jfree.chart.renderer.xy.XYItemRenderer, org.jfree.util.PublicCloneable
public class VStarPlotDataRenderer
extends org.jfree.chart.renderer.xy.XYErrorRenderer

This is VStar's plot data-point renderer. We subclass XYErrorRenderer in order to be able to plot error bars. TODO: Should we instead use StatisticalLineAndShapeRenderer (at least for means plot)? We override DATAPOINT_SHAPE rendering methods.
